==Documentation==
Helper template for rendering individual game items in the franchise games list.
Called by SMW #ask query in FranchiseEnd template.

===Parameters===
* <code>1</code> - Page title (full path like Games/Doom)
* <code>name</code> - Game display name
* <code>date</code> - Release date
* <code>platforms</code> - Platform names
* <code>image</code> - Cover image filename
</noinclude><includeonly><div class="gb-franchise-game-item">
<div class="gb-franchise-game-cover">[[{{{1}}}|<span class="gb-franchise-game-cover-placeholder"></span>]]</div>
<div class="gb-franchise-game-info">
<div class="gb-franchise-game-title">[[{{{1}}}|{{{name|{{#titleparts:{{{1}}}|1|2}}}}}]]</div>
<div class="gb-franchise-game-date">{{{date|}}}</div>
</div>
<div class="gb-franchise-game-platforms">{{#arraymap:{{{platforms|}}}|,|@@|<span class="gb-franchise-game-platform">[[Platforms/@@|@@]]</span>|}}</div>
</div></includeonly>
